=== Chronic Cough
<subsec:chronic-cough>

*Clinical Presentation.*

    - Persistent dry cough without infection
    - Throat irritation or tickle sensation
    - Cough worsening with exertion, talking, or breathing cold air
    - May be related to GERD, postnasal drip, or airway hypersensitivity
